posts.caption:
Are you interested in working with a like-minded, motivated and skilled team to develop a product or business in one weekend? If this sounds like you, this is the event for you!
=================================
Tickets Available at: https://swalex3.eventbrite.com/
=================================
NOW you can snag an EARLY BIRD TICKET to the third #SWAlex event before prices go up on October 10th, 2013! Don't miss out on the hugely discounted price and snag a ticket right now & be a part of the Global Startup Battle during the Global Entrepreneurship Week.

Students: $25 or 175EGP.
Developers, Designers, & Non-Technical: $40 or 275EGP.
Professionals: $100 or 690EGP

For more information feel free to contact us directly or visit our website: http://alexandria.startupweekend.org/  
Startup Weekend: http://www.startupweekend.org
Global Startup Battle: http://globalstartupbattle.co/
Global Entrepreneurship Week: http://www.unleashingideas.org/
